reviewText: Wonderful movie --brings back memory of old when grandmas and mothers instilled character, respect and love in their children.  If you enjoy great gospel --you will enjoy this powerful film.

This documentary is a must have for anyone that loves and follow Gospel Music.  I've always enjoyed the Barrett Sisters style and searched the internet relentlessly for any available CDs or DVDs,  Thanks to all that made this DVD possible.  This is truly a lovely piece of art.  Bivens, Durham, nc
My mother-in-law loves the Barrett Sisters.  She could not find this anywhere.  I found it and she loves this DVD.

A must have for those whom collect, and do research about the golden age of gospel music! Many golden nuggets about the era and the illustrious ministry of Delois Barrett Campbell & her sisters " The Barrett Sisters."
